name: ZurichParking
0:
”Alexa, ask Zurich Parking to find free spaces in Urania.”
”Alexa, ask Zurich Parking to list available parking garages.”
”Alexa, ask Zurich Parking to list the top five.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: zurich parking
des:
This skill allows you to find available parking in Zürich, Switzerland by asking for the number of currently available spaces in the over 37 available parking garages. Zurich Parking will tell you if the parking is currently open and if so, how many spaces are available.
Zurich Parking also allows you to list all parking garages in Zürich and sends you the list to your Alexa companion app.
Zurich Parking can tell you the current top five parkings by number of available spaces.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
